---
// CoreWeave-inspired hero component
---

<div class="cw-hero">
  <div class="cw-hero-content">
    <div class="cw-hero-text">
      <h1 class="cw-gradient-text">
        Build Documentation 
        <br />That Performs
      </h1>
      <p class="cw-hero-tagline">
        Create fast, accessible, and beautiful documentation websites with the power of Astro and Starlight. 
        Experience enterprise-grade performance with developer-friendly simplicity.
      </p>
      <div class="cw-hero-actions">
        <a href="/getting-started/" class="cw-button cw-button-primary">
          Get Started
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M6 12L10 8L6 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/withastro/starlight" class="cw-button cw-button-outline">
          View on GitHub
